[FolderBrowserDialogCrash.zip](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/18885106/FolderBrowserDialogCrash.zip)

### .NET version

8.0.405

### Did it work in .NET Framework?

Yes

### Did it work in any of the earlier releases of .NET Core or .NET 5+?

_No response_

### Issue description

`FolderBrowserDialog.ShowDialog()` crashes if `SelectedPath` contains ellipsis.

``` csharp
    public partial class Form1 : Form
    {
        public Form1()
        {
            string? result = SelectPath(@"C:\temp\..\temp");
        }

        private string? SelectPath(string path)
        {
            using var dialog = new FolderBrowserDialog();
            dialog.SelectedPath = path;
            var result = dialog.ShowDialog();
            return result == DialogResult.OK ? dialog.SelectedPath : null;
        }
    }
```
